title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return user recognizable strings
OB: When calling the 'get column label' method on the meta data object, the labels returned are null. However, after the extraction process, the labels should be recognizable strings.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Create a meta data object.
2. Call the 'get column label' method on the meta data object.
3. Verify that the labels returned are null.
